name: Sprawl 1
description: A playful visualization of growth and renewal, by San Francisco artist Zai Divecha. ⫸ This looping stop-motion video features handmade, physical paper sculptures and original sound design. ⫸ MP4, 4000x6000 px, 2021, edition of 20. ⫸ 10% of first sales will be donated to The Anti Police-Terror Project, a Black-led coalition in Northern California that seeks to build a replicable and sustainable model to eradicate police terror in communities of color. ⫸ @zaidivecha, zaidivecha.com
